## Description développeur
Composant généré par le pipeline IA avec fidélité pixel-perfect Figma. À compléter par le développeur.

## Token Mapping (Figma → CSS)
| Propriété CSS | Token | Figma (valeur exacte) | État |
|---|---|---|---|
| border-radius | var(--component-button-radius) → var(--semantic-radius-md) | 8px | tous |
| font-family | var(--component-button-font-family) → var(--semantic-font-family-default) | Inter | tous |
| font-weight | var(--component-button-font-weight) → var(--semantic-font-weight-semibold) | 600 | tous |
| transition | var(--component-button-transition) | all 150ms ease-in-out | tous |
| outline-width (focus) | var(--component-button-focus-ring-width) | 2px | :focus-visible |
| outline-offset (focus) | var(--component-button-focus-ring-offset) | 2px | :focus-visible |
| outline-color (focus) | var(--component-button-focus-ring-color) → var(--semantic-color-primary-500) | #d90a79 (color.primary.500) | :focus-visible |
| — SIZE SM — | | | |
| padding | var(--component-button-size-sm-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-sm-padding-x) | 4px 8px | sm |
| gap | var(--component-button-size-sm-gap) | 4px | sm |
| min-height | var(--component-button-size-sm-min-height) | 32px (token) / Figma height: 25px | sm |
| font-size | var(--component-button-size-sm-font-size) | 14px | sm |
| line-height | var(--component-button-size-sm-line-height) | 17px (Figma) / normal (token) | sm |
| — SIZE MD — | | | |
| padding | var(--component-button-size-md-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-md-padding-x) | 8px 16px | md |
| gap | var(--component-button-size-md-gap) | 8px | md |
| min-height | var(--component-button-size-md-min-height) | 40px (token) / Figma height: 33px | md |
| font-size | var(--component-button-size-md-font-size) | 14px | md |
| line-height | var(--component-button-size-md-line-height) | 17px (Figma) / normal (token) | md |
| — SIZE LG — | | | |
| padding | var(--component-button-size-lg-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-lg-padding-x) | 8px 24px | lg |
| gap | var(--component-button-size-lg-gap) | 8px | lg |
| min-height | var(--component-button-size-lg-min-height) | 48px (token) / Figma height: 35px | lg |
| font-size | var(--component-button-size-lg-font-size) | 16px | lg |
| line-height | var(--component-button-size-lg-line-height) | 19px (Figma) / normal (token) | lg |
| — TYPE PRIMARY — | | | |
| background-color | var(--component-button-primary-bg) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #d90a79 | default |
| color | var(--component-button-primary-color) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #ffffff | default |
| background-color | var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #b91c1c | hover |
| background-color | var(--component-button-primary-bg-active) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #991b1b | active |
| background-color | var(--component-button-primary-bg-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #f3f4f6 | disabled |
| color | var(--component-button-primary-color-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #d1d5db | disabled |
| — TYPE SECONDARY — | | | |
| background-color | var(--component-button-secondary-bg) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #ffffff | default |
| color | var(--component-button-secondary-color) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #374151 | default |
| background-color | var(--component-button-secondary-bg-hover) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #f9fafb | hover |
| background-color | var(--component-button-secondary-bg-active) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #f3f4f6 | active |
| background-color | var(--component-button-secondary-bg-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #f9fafb | disabled |
| color | var(--component-button-secondary-color-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #d1d5db | disabled |
| — TYPE GHOST — | | | |
| background-color | var(--component-button-ghost-bg) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | transparent | default |
| color | var(--component-button-ghost-color) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #374151 | default |
| background-color | var(--component-button-ghost-bg-hover) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #f3f4f6 | hover |
| background-color | var(--component-button-ghost-bg-active) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #e5e7eb | active |
| background-color | var(--component-button-ghost-bg-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | transparent | disabled |
| color | var(--component-button-ghost-color-disabled) ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT | #d1d5db | disabled |

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser les CSS custom properties (var(--component-*))
- Respecter les états interactifs (hover, active, focus, disabled)
- Vérifier la fidélité visuelle avec la maquette Figma

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser de valeurs brutes (px, #hex) — utiliser les tokens
- Ne pas supprimer les états d'accessibilité (:focus-visible)
- Ne pas modifier les dimensions sans vérifier la spec Figma

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const css = `/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   COMPONENT TOKEN DEFINITIONS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
:root {
  /* Radius */
  --component-button-radius: var(--semantic-radius-md, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);

  /* Typography */
  --component-button-font-family: var(--semantic-font-family-default, /* FALLBACK */ 'Inter', sans-serif);
  --component-button-font-weight: var(--semantic-font-weight-semibold, /* FALLBACK */ 600);
  --component-button-transition: all 150ms ease-in-out;

  /* Focus ring */
  --component-button-focus-ring-width: 2px;
  --component-button-focus-ring-offset: 2px;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.focus.ringColor — Figma: #d90a79 */
  --component-button-focus-ring-color: var(--semantic-color-primary-500, /* FALLBACK */ #d90a79);

  /* ── Size: SM ── */
  --component-button-size-sm-padding-x: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  --component-button-size-sm-padding-y: var(--spacing-xs, /* FALLBACK */ 4px);
  --component-button-size-sm-gap: var(--spacing-xs, /* FALLBACK */ 4px);
  --component-button-size-sm-font-size: var(--font-size-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 14px);
  --component-button-size-sm-line-height: var(--font-line-height-normal, /* FALLBACK */ 17px);
  --component-button-size-sm-min-height: 32px; /* token: 32px / Figma rendered height: 25px */

  /* ── Size: MD ── */
  --component-button-size-md-padding-x: var(--spacing-md, /* FALLBACK */ 16px);
  --component-button-size-md-padding-y: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  --component-button-size-md-gap: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  --component-button-size-md-font-size: var(--font-size-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 14px);
  --component-button-size-md-line-height: var(--font-line-height-normal, /* FALLBACK */ 17px);
  --component-button-size-md-min-height: 40px; /* token: 40px / Figma rendered height: 33px */

  /* ── Size: LG ── */
  --component-button-size-lg-padding-x: var(--spacing-lg, /* FALLBACK */ 24px);
  --component-button-size-lg-padding-y: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  --component-button-size-lg-gap: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  --component-button-size-lg-font-size: var(--font-size-md, /* FALLBACK */ 16px);
  --component-button-size-lg-line-height: var(--font-line-height-normal, /* FALLBACK */ 19px);
  --component-button-size-lg-min-height: 48px; /* token: 48px / Figma rendered height: 35px */

  /* ── Type: Primary ── */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg — Figma: #d90a79 */
  --component-button-primary-bg: var(--semantic-color-primary-default, /* FALLBACK */ #d90a79);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.color — Figma: #ffffff */
  --component-button-primary-color: var(--semantic-color-on-primary, /* FALLBACK */ #ffffff);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg-hover — Figma: #b91c1c */
  --component-button-primary-bg-hover: var(--semantic-color-primary-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #b91c1c);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg-active — Figma: #991b1b */
  --component-button-primary-bg-active: var(--semantic-color-primary-active, /* FALLBACK */ #991b1b);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg-disabled — Figma: #f3f4f6 */
  --component-button-primary-bg-disabled: var(--semantic-color-surface-disabled, /* FALLBACK */ #f3f4f6);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.color-disabled — Figma: #d1d5db */
  --component-button-primary-color-disabled: var(--semantic-color-text-disabled, /* FALLBACK */ #d1d5db);

  /* ── Type: Secondary ── */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg — Figma: #ffffff */
  --component-button-secondary-bg: var(--semantic-color-surface-default, /* FALLBACK */ #ffffff);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.color — Figma: #374151 */
  --component-button-secondary-color: var(--semantic-color-text-default, /* FALLBACK */ #374151);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg-hover — Figma: #f9fafb */
  --component-button-secondary-bg-hover: var(--semantic-color-surface-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #f9fafb);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg-active — Figma: #f3f4f6 */
  --component-button-secondary-bg-active: var(--semantic-color-surface-active, /* FALLBACK */ #f3f4f6);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg-disabled — Figma: #f9fafb */
  --component-button-secondary-bg-disabled: var(--semantic-color-surface-disabled-subtle, /* FALLBACK */ #f9fafb);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.color-disabled — Figma: #d1d5db */
  --component-button-secondary-color-disabled: var(--semantic-color-text-disabled, /* FALLBACK */ #d1d5db);

  /* ── Type: Ghost ── */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg — Figma: transparent */
  --component-button-ghost-bg: transparent;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.color — Figma: #374151 */
  --component-button-ghost-color: var(--semantic-color-text-default, /* FALLBACK */ #374151);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg-hover — Figma: #f3f4f6 */
  --component-button-ghost-bg-hover: var(--semantic-color-surface-ghost-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #f3f4f6);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg-active — Figma: #e5e7eb */
  --component-button-ghost-bg-active: var(--semantic-color-surface-ghost-active, /* FALLBACK */ #e5e7eb);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg-disabled — Figma: transparent */
  --component-button-ghost-bg-disabled: transparent;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.color-disabled — Figma: #d1d5db */
  --component-button-ghost-color-disabled: var(--semantic-color-text-disabled, /* FALLBACK */ #d1d5db);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   BASE BLOCK
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button {
  /* Layout — auto-layout HORIZONTAL */
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--component-button-size-md-gap);

  /* Sizing */
  min-height: var(--component-button-size-md-min-height);
  padding: var(--component-button-size-md-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-md-padding-x);

  /* Typography */
  font-family: var(--component-button-font-family);
  font-size: var(--component-button-size-md-font-size);
  font-weight: var(--component-button-font-weight);
  line-height: var(--component-button-size-md-line-height);

  /* Appearance */
  border-radius: var(--component-button-radius);
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  outline: none;

  /* Transition */
  transition: var(--component-button-transition);

  /* Reset */
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}

/* ── Focus visible (all types) ── */
.button:focus-visible {
  outline: var(--component-button-focus-ring-width) solid var(--component-button-focus-ring-color);
  outline-offset: var(--component-button-focus-ring-offset);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   SIZE MODIFIERS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button--sm {
  gap: var(--component-button-size-sm-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-size-sm-min-height);
  padding: var(--component-button-size-sm-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-sm-padding-x);
  font-size: var(--component-button-size-sm-font-size);
  line-height: var(--component-button-size-sm-line-height);
}

.button--md {
  gap: var(--component-button-size-md-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-size-md-min-height);
  padding: var(--component-button-size-md-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-md-padding-x);
  font-size: var(--component-button-size-md-font-size);
  line-height: var(--component-button-size-md-line-height);
}

.button--lg {
  gap: var(--component-button-size-lg-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-size-lg-min-height);
  padding: var(--component-button-size-lg-padding-y) var(--component-button-size-lg-padding-x);
  font-size: var(--component-button-size-lg-font-size);
  line-height: var(--component-button-size-lg-line-height);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   TYPE: PRIMARY
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button--primary {
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg);
  color: var(--component-button-primary-color);
}

.button--primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover);
}

.button--primary:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-active);
}

.button--primary:disabled,
.button--primary[aria-disabled="true"] {
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-disabled);
  color: var(--component-button-primary-color-disabled);
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   TYPE: SECONDARY
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button--secondary {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg);
  color: var(--component-button-secondary-color);
}

.button--secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-hover);
}

.button--secondary:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-active);
}

.button--secondary:disabled,
.button--secondary[aria-disabled="true"] {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-disabled);
  color: var(--component-button-secondary-color-disabled);
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   TYPE: GHOST
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button--ghost {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg);
  color: var(--component-button-ghost-color);
}

.button--ghost:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-hover);
}

.button--ghost:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-active);
}

.button--ghost:disabled,
.button--ghost[aria-disabled="true"] {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-disabled);
  color: var(--component-button-ghost-color-disabled);
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   ICON SLOT
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button__icon {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.button--sm .button__icon {
  width: 16px; /* Figma: 16px */
  height: 16px;
}

.button--md .button__icon {
  width: 20px; /* Figma: 20px */
  height: 20px;
}

.button--lg .button__icon {
  width: 24px; /* Figma: 24px */
  height: 24px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   STORYBOOK DEMO UTILITY CLASSES
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.button-demo {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 32px;
  padding: 32px;
  background: #f8f9fa;
  font-family: var(--component-button-font-family);
}

.button-demo__section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.button-demo__label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #6b7280;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
}

.button-demo__row {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
}`;

const Demo = () => (<div style={{ padding: "24px" }}><style>{css}</style><div>Component preview</div></div>);

render(<Demo />);
```

